---
/**
 * The medical disclaimer every treatment page carries (CLAUDE.md hard
 * constraint 3). Injected by TreatmentLayout unconditionally — pages
 * cannot opt out. Rendered on the LIGHT surface, before the closing dark
 * band, so it never dissolves into the footer.
 */
---

<aside class="disclaimer" aria-label="Medical disclaimer">
  <p>
    <strong>Medical disclaimer.</strong> The content on this page is general information and
    education. It is not medical advice, and it does not replace an in-person evaluation. Whether a
    treatment fits your needs is decided together with Amy Palacios, FNP, during a consultation.
    Individual experiences vary.
  </p>
</aside>

<style is:global>
  .disclaimer {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ng-pink-300);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--ng-ink-900);
  }
</style>
